#: expressions/base.py:29
msgid "Path to the **reference** audio file"
msgstr "参考音频文件路径"

#: expressions/base.py:30
msgid "Path to the **UTAU** audio file"
msgstr "歌姬音频文件路径"

#: expressions/base.py:31
msgid "Path to the `.ustx` project file to be processed"
msgstr "要处理的 USTX 项目文件路径"

#: expressions/base.py:32
msgid "**Track number** to apply expressions to (1-based index)"
msgstr "要导入表情参数的音轨编号（从 1 开始）"

#: expressions/base.py:33
msgid ""
"**Start time** of the **reference** audio (format `M:S`, e.g. `0:10.01`)."
" Omit to specify the beginning"
msgstr "**参考音频**的**起始时间戳**（格式 `分:秒`，如`0:10.01`表示`0分10.01秒`）。不指定此参数则默认为音频开头处"

#: expressions/base.py:34
msgid ""
"**End time** of the **reference** audio (format `M:S`, e.g. `0:10.01`). "
"Omit to specify the ending"
msgstr "**参考音频**的**结束时间戳**（格式 `分:秒`，如`0:10.01`表示`0分10.01秒`）。不指定此参数则默认为音频结尾处"

#: expressions/base.py:35
msgid ""
"**Start time** of the **UTAU** audio (format `M:S`, e.g. `0:10.01`). Omit"
" to specify the beginning"
msgstr "**歌姬音频**的**起始时间戳**（格式 `分:秒`，如`0:10.01`表示`0分10.01秒`）。不指定此参数则默认为音频开头处"

#: expressions/base.py:36
msgid ""
"**End time** of the **UTAU** audio (format `M:S`, e.g. `0:10.01`). Omit "
"to specify the ending"
msgstr "**歌姬音频**的**结束时间戳**（格式 `分:秒`，如`0:10.01`表示`0分10.01秒`）。不指定此参数则默认为音频结尾处"

#: expressions/base.py:58
#, python-brace-format
msgid "ref  [{} → {}] {:.3f}s"
msgstr "参考音频选段：[{} → {}] 共{:.3f}秒"

#: expressions/base.py:66
#, python-brace-format
msgid "utau [{} → {}] {:.3f}s"
msgstr "歌姬音频选段：[{} → {}] 共{:.3f}秒"

#: expressions/base.py:73
msgid "Initialization complete."
msgstr "初始化完成。"

#: expressions/base.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Expression written to USTX file: '{}'"
msgstr "表情参数已写入 USTX 文件：'{}'"

#: expressions/base.py:92
msgid "Expression result is empty. Skipping USTX update."
msgstr "表情参数结果为空，USTX 文件将不会更新。"

#: expressions/dyn.py:21
msgid "Dynamics (curve)"
msgstr "动态曲线 Dynamics (curve)"

#: expressions/dyn.py:23 expressions/tenc.py:23
msgid ""
"**Trim silence** from the leading and trailing edges of the audio before "
"extracting expression"
msgstr ""
"在提取表情特征前，**剪除**音频开头与结尾的**静音部分**"

#: expressions/dyn.py:24 expressions/pitd.py:34 expressions/tenc.py:24
msgid ""
"**Radius** for the FastDTW alignment algorithm; larger values allow more "
"flexible alignment but increase computation time"
msgstr "FastDTW 对齐算法的**半径**；值越大对齐越灵活，但计算时间也越长"

#: expressions/dyn.py:25 expressions/pitd.py:36 expressions/tenc.py:25
msgid ""
"Controls the **smoothness** of the expression curve using Gaussian "
"filtering. Higher values produce smoother curves but may lose fine detail"
msgstr "通过高斯滤波控制表情曲线的**平滑度**；值越大曲线越平滑，但可能丢失细节"

#: expressions/dyn.py:26 expressions/pitd.py:37 expressions/tenc.py:26
msgid ""
"**Scaling factor** applied to the expression curve. Values >1 amplify the"
" expression, =1 keeps original intensity, <1 reduces it"
msgstr "应用于表情曲线的**缩放因子**；大于 1 则放大，等于 1 则保持原强度，小于 1 则缩小"

#: expressions/dyn.py:36 expressions/pitd.py:50 expressions/tenc.py:38
msgid "Extracting expression..."
msgstr "正在提取表情参数..."

#: expressions/dyn.py:67 expressions/pitd.py:104 expressions/tenc.py:69
msgid "Expression extraction complete."
msgstr "表情参数提取完成。"

#: expressions/pitd.py:23
msgid "Pitch Deviation (curve)"
msgstr "音高偏差曲线 Pitch Deviation (curve)"

#: expressions/pitd.py:25
msgid "fast, CPU-based (ONNX Runtime)"
msgstr "快速，基于 CPU（ONNX Runtime）"

#: expressions/pitd.py:26
msgid "classic but slow, CPU & NVIDIA GPU (TensorFlow)"
msgstr "经典但较慢，支持 CPU 和 NVIDIA GPU（TensorFlow）"

#: expressions/pitd.py:31
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**F0 detection backend** for extracting pitch from WAV files. Available "
"options:\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"从 WAV 文件提取音高所用的 **F0 检测后端**，可选项如下：\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"

#: expressions/pitd.py:32
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Minimum **confidence level** for keeping detected pitch values in the "
"**UTAU** WAV. Lower values retain more frames but may include errors. "
"Omit to use the recommended value for the selected backend:\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"提取**歌姬**音频音高时保留检测值所需的最低**置信度**；值越低保留帧越多，但可能引入误差。忽略该参数则使用所选后端的推荐值：\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"

#: expressions/pitd.py:33
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Minimum **confidence level** for keeping detected pitch values in the "
"**reference** WAV. Lower values retain more frames but may include "
"errors. Omit to use the recommended value for the selected backend:\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"提取**参考**音频音高时保留检测值所需的最低**置信度**；值越低保留帧越多，但可能引入误差。忽略该参数则使用所选后端的推荐值：\n"
"\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"

#: expressions/pitd.py:35
msgid ""
"**Semitone shift** between the UTAU and reference WAV. If the UTAU WAV is"
" an octave higher than the reference WAV, set to 12; if lower, set to "
"-12. Omit to enable automatic shift estimation"
msgstr "歌姬音频与参考音频之间的**半音偏移**；若歌姬比参考高一个八度则设为 12，低一个八度则设为 -12；忽略该参数则启用自动估算"

#: expressions/pitd.py:180
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Estimated Semitone-shift: {}"
msgstr "估计的半音偏移：{}"

#: expressions/tenc.py:21
msgid "Tension (curve)"
msgstr "张力曲线 Tension (curve)"

#: expressions/tenc.py:27
msgid ""
"**Bias** offset added to the expression curve. Positive values shift the "
"curve upward; negative values shift it downward"
msgstr "添加到表情曲线的**偏置**偏移量；正值使曲线上移，负值使曲线下移"

